This paper discusses the implementation of agile practices in a large-scale software development project, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. The paper also touches upon project management (cs.SD), software development process (cs.PL), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and distributed computing (cs.DC) topics, making these sub-categories likely as well.
